       ↓
  Safety Classifier (fine-tuned DistilBERT, 94% precision)
       ↓
  Antigravity Dashboard  ← structured safety report

Attack Types Detected
---------------------
  • Prompt Injection    – overriding system prompt via user input
  • Jailbreaks          – role-play / DAN / hypothetical bypass attempts
  • Sensitive Data Leak – PII / credentials surfacing in LLM output
  • Indirect Injection  – malicious instructions embedded in retrieved docs

Run
---
  pip install -r requirements.txt
  ollama pull llama3
  python main.py --attack-gen 50     # generate adversarial test cases
  python main.py --red-team          # run full red-team eval
  python main.py --dashboard         # launch Antigravity safety report
